ygData.subject: Will trade powerleveling on Karana
ygData.msgSnippet: Hi, I have a level 30 Barb Shaman on Karana. I have other characters I d like to get to 20 or so. If you have a higher level character maybe we could swap
ygData.messageBody:
Hi, I have a level 30 Barb Shaman on Karana. I
have other characters I'd like to get to 20 or so. If
you have a higher level character maybe we could swap
leveling sessions. <br><br>Contact me or email me if that
would interest you. Also I am in Pacific timezone and
play in the evening about 3 days a week. I'm not
really a big fan of powerleveling, but my time is a
consideration. My Shaman has about 30 days played, so I've paid
my dues, so to speak.
